Conditionals and Flow

n <- 10

if(n < 10) { 
  print("n is less than 10")
  
} else if (n >10) { 
    print("n is greater than 10")
}else { 
    "n is equal to 10"
  }


for (n in seq(0,20)) {
  if(n < 10) { 
    print("n is less than 10")
  
  } else if (n >10) { 
      print("n is greater than 10")
  }else { 
      "n is equal to 10"
  }
}  
g <- 0

while (g<=10) {
  print(paste(g, "is less than or equal to 10"))
  g <- g+1 
}
